    <bcl:section id="d2e34" toc="false">
      <bcl:marginalnote>Powers and duties of natural resource officers</bcl:marginalnote>
      <bcl:num>1</bcl:num>
      <bcl:text>For the purposes of section 3 (1) (a) of the <bcl:link resource="leg" xlink:href="/legislation/11021_01" xlink:type="locator"><in:doc>Natural Resource Compliance Act</in:doc></bcl:link>, a natural resource officer may exercise the powers and perform the duties of the official listed in Column 1 of the Table under the enactment set out opposite in Column 2.</bcl:text>
    </bcl:section>
    <bcl:section id="d2e49">
